<h2 class="bold font-l">Slayers</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Lina Inverse has her powers of magic reduced by 99.99% for a few days due to her &quot;Time of the Month&quot;, and this happens to ALL female magic wielders. </p>
</div>
